{"about_the_game":"Jump into a world where monsters are everywhere, and it's up to you to stop them! <br>-A flexible game that you can play as your main activity or enjoy casually while working or playing other games.<br><br><strong>Create your own builds:</strong><br>There are various upgrading systems in this game, including: unlocking random gears, obtaining powerful passives, and utilizing the skill tree. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2562730/extras/ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1730021901\" /><br><br><u><strong>Key features:</strong></u><br><br><strong>Unique Towers:</strong> Choose from a different set of towers, each with its special way of attacking and upgrading.<br><br><strong>Roguelike Elements:</strong> With random rewards and various passives and upgrades, no two resets will feel the same.<br><br><strong>Skill Tree:</strong> Spend skill points on new upgrades to boost your gameplay. With six paths filled with skills, you can customize your game experience.<br><br><strong>Offline Progress: </strong>When you exit the game, your towers will keep farming for you. When you come back you will find all the precious rewards they found<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2562730/extras/offlineGif.gif?t=1730021901\" /><br><br><strong>Two Layers of Prestige</strong>: Unlock three new contents, The Champion, Shards of Valor and Books of Powers to significantly improve your power.<br><br><strong>The Automator</strong>: A feature that plays the game for you, unlocks towers and purchases upgrades by itself.<br><br><strong>And many more</strong>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Explorer 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2562730/13ea2c01cc7f864621280f8939d4a6dc750b62cb.jpg"},{"name":"Explorer 2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2562730/13ea2c01cc7f86